description: When I actually do a job,\nI do it properly!
Whew...\nThat should be the end of\nmy work for today.
And that's a wrap.\nWho knew I could take care\nof all this on my own?
All right!\nNow I finally have a chance\nto slack off...
If you want the cheese so bad,\ngo earn a proper living wage\nand buy it from us!
Now you see what happens\nwhen you make an enemy\nout of me!
I'm more effective than\nyou'd think, aren't I?
Man, I'm pooped...\nWhy do they have to scurry\naround so fast...?
At this rate,\nMahy's gonna give me\na huge telling-off!
I thought I was working\npretty hard, too...\nHow did this happen?!
They got me...\nMice are trickier little beasts\nthan I thought.
Curse you, mice...!\nHow dare you steal\nmy delicious cheese?!
So... tired...\nBut next time, I swear\nI'll keep the cheese safe...
